data.description:
At 2,897 sq/ft , this large and very spacious 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom home is for rent in the desirable East Sanoma Ranch area. Beautiful view of the Organ Mountains driving into quiet cul-de-sac. 2 car garage. Spacious rooms with walk in closets. Great room in entry of the house that could be used as another living, game room, den or office area! Large open concept for family room, kitchen and dinning room with tile floors. Fireplace in family room and upstairs master bedroom. Jet tub in master bathroom. Updated faucets for kitchen and bathroom sinks. Beautiful view of the Organ Mountains from master bedroom. Central air for cooling and forced air heating. Wet bar. Washer and dryer included. Backyard oasis of oleander trees for privacy.
Close to Dona Ana Community College, Walmart Super Center, Walgreens and many restaurants. Close to freeway access. Short distance drive to Organ Mountains.

This is for a 6 month lease. Renter is responsible for all utilities. Owner provides maintenance of front and back yards.
Small dogs allowed. No smoking. Washer and dryer is included.
